    "db_statements": ["a case of dispute which involves, on the one hand, the Ẓillu’s-Sulṭán... and, on the other, Mírzá Fatḥ-‘Alí Ḵhán, the Ṣáḥib-i-Díván."],
    "mention_idxs": [321]
  },
  {
    "canonical_name": "Siyyid-i-S̱his̱h-Parí",
    "entity_type": "person",
